---
import HeadingLarge from "@components/HeadingLarge.astro";
import Text from "@components/Text.astro";
import View from "@components/View.astro";
import Group from "@components/Group.astro";
import { Layout } from "@layouts";
import Image from "@components/Image.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Starboard | Jonathon Toon | Software Designer, Product Leader"
  description="Jonathon Toon is a versatile software designer and product leader based in Aotearoa New Zealand."
  keywords="design, software, product, fractional, leadership, new zealand, aotearoa, technology, typescript, start ups, engineering, mentorship, coaching, adplist"
  twitterHandle="@jonathontoon"
  canonicalUrl="https://www.jonathontoon.com/"
  ogImage="/images/og-image.png"
>
  <Group>
    <HeadingLarge class="px-2">Starboard</HeadingLarge>
    <Text class="px-2">
      Starboard is a maritime intelligence platform processing 4,000+ vessel
      positions per second for government agencies across New Zealand,
      Australia, and the Pacific.
    </Text>
    <Text class="px-2">
      As they expanded globally, the website wasn't helping prospects find
      relevant information about how the platform solved their specific
      challenges. I partnered with the Chief of Product and Chief of Marketing
      to rethink their web experience and product positioning.
    </Text>
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <View class="px-2">
      <View class="h-px w-full bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-700" />
    </View>
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <Text class="px-2">
      Through a content audit with Sales and Customer Success, it became clear that prospects wanted to see case studies before technical specs. The existing site buried this social proof under generic product descriptions.
    </Text>
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <Image
      src="/images/work/starboard-website-one.png"
      alt="Homepage design showcasing maritime surveillance expertise and global reach."
      class="w-full rounded-xl bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-800"
      lightbox={true}
    />
    <Image
      src="/images/work/starboard-website-two.png"
      alt="Solutions page highlighting real-time vessel tracking and analytics capabilities."
      class="w-full rounded-xl bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-800"
      lightbox={true}
    />
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <Text class="px-2">
      I designed and built 20+ pages on Webflow, migrating 100+ existing
      articles while creating targeted landing experiences for different use
      cases. The 3-month redesign delivered clearer positioning and faster
      qualification of prospects.
    </Text>
  </Group>
  <Group>
    <Image
      src="/images/work/starboard-website-three.png"
      alt="Resource center design organizing maritime intelligence insights and case studies."
      class="w-full rounded-xl bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-800"
      lightbox={true}
    />
    <Image
      src="/images/work/starboard-website-four.png"
      alt="About page emphasizing team expertise and company mission in ocean protection."
      class="w-full rounded-xl bg-stone-200 dark:bg-stone-800"
      lightbox={true}
    />
  </Group>
</Layout>
